						<summary>

						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Prabhava (wrong for Vibhava 1638 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers the gift of two villages Isanakūr and Nāṇakūr to Śrīnivāsayya to meet the expenses of worship and <hi rend="italic">sahasranāma-archana</hi> etc., to god, for the merit of Muddammagāru, queen of Śrīraṅga Kṛishṇa-Mudduvīrappa-Nāyaka. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Prabhava, Āshāḍha, śu. 5, Friday</hi> regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1688, June 22, Friday, the cyclic year being Vibhava.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
